{"tid":2387257,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Fate動畫版製作公司拖糧唔找數 被作畫監督開名告發","createTime":"2021-01-30T07:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T10:12:06.000Z","uid":4618,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef91cb06f284d65d064f7088b98a15c5d757c6b","tid":2387257,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:34:46.000Z","msg":"「劇場版FGO」アニメ制作会社が下請法違反、公取が指導 「被害」の作画監督が実名告発「あまりにひどい状況」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/c2fbed2909813645c5da4f26d58ba5bd6864800d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.yahoo.co.jp%2Farticles%2Fc2fbed2909813645c5da4f26d58ba5bd6864800d&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjFTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=15b6d434\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/c2fbed2909813645c5da4f26d58ba5bd6864800d</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAJ72yE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaAJ72yE.jpg&h=ae0978a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係fgo 6章劇場版製作公司之一「Signal-MD」<br />\n<br />\n口頭講好位作畫監督久高司郎人工係36萬，但淨返一半遲遲未俾，仲要向佢惡言相向<br />\n<br />\n之後久高去搵勞工署，上年2月經協助轉介實名上告「公正取引委員会」，早幾日出咗調查結果指明Signal-MD違反「下請法」(類似承包法)<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kudaka1s/status/1353910884779757569?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkudaka1s%2Fstatus%2F1353910884779757569%3Fs%3D21&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjFTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=60867b92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkudaka1s%2Fstatus%2F1353910884779757569%3Fs%3D21&h=a6ffe783\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kudaka1s/status/1353910884779757569?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"6ea580fb73c63db95242ea6111d52072afd508ad","tid":2387257,"uid":4618,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外位被拖糧既作畫監督早幾日出咗條tweet<br />\n<br />\n依家動畫企畫涉及外資，最大問題係嚟自中國資本。因為唔俾共產黨審查冇可能通過，而且通常需時三個月。<br />\n本來動畫製作已經工期緊張，咁搞法最後成品無聊就係現狀。呢樣對佢嚟講係可怕既屈辱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kudaka1s/status/1354216542821441542?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkudaka1s%2Fstatus%2F1354216542821441542%3Fs%3D21&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjFTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=dc553151\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkudaka1s%2Fstatus%2F1354216542821441542%3Fs%3D21&h=f45a307c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kudaka1s/status/1354216542821441542?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kudaka1s/status/1354216937409056768?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkudaka1s%2Fstatus%2F1354216937409056768%3Fs%3D21&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjFTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=ac23ed47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkudaka1s%2Fstatus%2F1354216937409056768%3Fs%3D21&h=2d8c3afd\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kudaka1s/status/1354216937409056768?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"764e564b3b911a423b36ab33bc72ac4f0734242b","tid":2387257,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:07:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾動畫冇所謂啦"},{"pid":"29c4f18126abc41ec7d2504c61a80b96f83a9e87","tid":2387257,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"764e564b3b911a423b36ab33bc72ac4f0734242b","tid":2387257,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:07:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾動畫冇所謂啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"Fate過氣了嗎"},{"pid":"1df01efcc56aff31c79be42c9296c9c315f9d462","tid":2387257,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://otakomu.jp/archives/25240087.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fotakomu.jp%2Farchives%2F25240087.html&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjFTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=e33d4c9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://otakomu.jp/archives/25240087.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪呢單<br />\n<br